        </mj-text> 
        <mj-image border-radius="10px" padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.longandshort.com/email/images/trump-media-moves-into-finance.png" alt="Trump Media and Technology Corp has filed a trademark for ETFs that will invest in 'Made in America' products" href="https://www.longandshort.com" />
        <mj-text padding="0px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#A9A7AF">
          <p style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.2; color: #A9A7AF;">Trump is seeking a new direct-to-voter megaphone ahead of a key legislative election this year. Credits: Chris DELMAS / AFP
          </p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5">Trump Media & Technology Corp. has filed to trademark <a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #6b705c; color: black;" href="https://link.longandshort.com/ls-07-02-2025-h1-1-six-investment-products" target="_blank">six investment products</a> under its new Truth.Fi financial platform. The company has partnered with Yorkville Advisors to oversee the approval and launch of these funds. The proposed investment products are ETFs that will invest in ‘Made in America’ products and provide an alternative to “woke funds.”</p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5">The financial industry has seen a growing divide over ESG (Environmental, Social, and Governance) investing as red states <a style="text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 2px solid  #6b705c; color: black;" href="https://link.longandshort.com/ls-07-02-2025-h1-2-push-back" target="_blank">push back</a> against responsible investing firms. This new trend by Trump’s company appears to capitalize on this trend by providing alternative investment strategies.</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="10px 12px" />
